name: JahanaHayes.com

subject: The situation and the solution
body: https://www.jahanahayes.com/ [https://www.jahanahayes.com/] Friend, here isthe situation: Allies of Donald Trump have poured resources into CT-05 as anew poll shows that Congresswoman Jahana Hayes is barely leading, 49%-46% ,within the polling margin of error. All while Trump is doubling down on hisrhetoric, excusing the January 6 insurrection, and threatening to use the U.S.military on his political opponents whom he calls “the enemy from within.” IfMAGA Republicans flip this seat red, it could destroy our hopes of taking backthe House — and send a dangerously unfit Republican to Congress instead of afighter for our communities like Jahana. Here is the solution: Early voting inConnecticut is underway. We have a busy week ahead of us organizing across thedistrict. We could use the extra resources to reach more voters if you canspare a few bucks today. Can you contribute $10 or any amount to help us turnout voters and reelect Jahana Hayes? The only poll that matters is the one onElection Day, and this race is looking razor-thin.[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/jh-em-nov2024?amount=10] If you've savedyour payment information with ActBlue Express, your donation will go throughimmediately: $5 → [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/jh-em-nov2024?express_lane=true&amount;=5] $10 →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/jh-em-nov2024?express_lane=true&amount;=10]$25 → [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/jh-em-nov2024?express_lane=true&amount;=25] $50 →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/jh-em-nov2024?express_lane=true&amount;=50]$100 → [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/jh-em-nov2024?express_lane=true&amount;=100] Other →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/jh-em-nov2024] There is not much time left,but your support — especially this close to Election Day — makes an enormousdifference. Thank you. — Team Hayes http://jahanahayes.com[http://jahanahayes.com] About Jahana Jahana Hayes proudly representsConnecticut's 5th Congressional district.
